works.description:
NLP Tips, Techniques, Information &  
Articles
Word/Percentage of page =  65/13% (Case No.68)

All of the techniques work to some extent if you follow them carefully -  

you may need to improvise a little at times. For example a lot of NLP  
techniques appear to rely heavily on having a great ability to visualise -
 
even though many people do not visualise very clearly. Here you simply  
pretend that you are visualising - and the techniques will work just as  
well!
